Move forward!

17
00:02:52,653 --> 00:02:53,927
Come forward!

18
00:02:58,813 --> 00:03:02,806
Keep your hands in the air and your
weapons visible at all times.

19
00:03:03,613 --> 00:03:05,524
Form up, in three columns...

20
00:03:05,853 --> 00:03:07,366
...across the square.

21
